        Q("MDT", "<p>MDT: free Windows deployment automation. Components: Deployment Workbench, task sequences, drivers, apps, boot images. Process: import WIM -> drivers -> task sequence -> update share -> boot ISO. WinPE: boot from PXE or USB. CustomSettings.ini: config database. Driver management: total control drivers by model. PXE boot: WDS to network boot WinPE. USMT: migrate user profiles. Refresh: reinstall while preserving data. Zero-touch: fully automated. Lite-touch: minimal interaction.</p>"),
