        Q("Hardware & Protocols", "<p>MCUs: ESP32, ESP8266, Raspberry Pi Pico W. Sensors: DHT22, BME280, PIR, HC-SR04, BH1750. Actuators: relays, servo, DC motor. Protocols: I2C, SPI, UART, 1-Wire. Wireless: WiFi, BLE, Zigbee, Z-Wave, LoRaWAN, Thread, Matter. MQTT: pub-sub broker (Mosquitto, EMQX), QoS 0/1/2. CoAP: REST-like UDP. Matter: smart home standard.</p>"),
