        Q("ROS 2 & Hardware", "<p>ROS 2: robot middleware. Nodes, topics, services, actions. TF: coordinate frames. URDF: robot model. RViz2: 3D visualization. Gazebo: physics sim. Micro-ROS: for MCUs. DDS: Fast DDS, Cyclone DDS. Robot types: differential drive, mecanum, manipulator. Kinematics: forward/inverse. Sensors: LiDAR, IMU, encoders, camera. Motors: DC+encoder, stepper, BLDC, servo. PID: tune for smooth control. Motor drivers: L298N, ODrive, Dynamixel.</p>"),
